  <li id="comment-10245" class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/01047639300653750871" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">flybynightkarmarepair</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/07/the-important-parts/#comment-10245"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-07-23T05:06:00-04:00">Wednesday, July 23, 2008 at 5:06 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>All the best pie crust recipes seem to require a food processor.  What are those of us who don&#8217;t have or want one to do?</p>
    </div>

