    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>As if you didn&#8217;t have enough comments on the Apricot Tart recipe already! Since there are literally thousands of mangos of various varieties heaped in piles along the road and in the markets I thought I&#8217;d substitute these &#8220;Sri Lankan apricots&#8221; for the Blenheims. I must say the result is pretty: a deep yellow, almost a mustard yellow in the fruit which I dusted with cinnamon before baking. Always enjoy your blog!</p>
    </div>

